docblock.description:
Sets defualt ordering for DB query
<code>
 <?php
    class Model_User extends Model{
         protected $order = array('email', 'DESC');
    }
 ?>
</code>

sets the primary key name
<code>
 <?php
    class Model_User extends Model{
         protected $primary_key = 'email';
    }
 ?>
</code>
